  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Once you reach 15th level, you can shield yourself and others with telekinetic force. As a bonus action, you can choose creatures, which can include you, that you can see within 30 feet of you, up to a number of creatures equal to your Intelligence modifier (minimum of one creature). Each of the chosen creatures is protected by half cover for 1 minute or until you are incapacitated.</p><p>Once you take this bonus action, you cannot do so again until you finish a long rest, unless you expend a Psionic Energy die to take it again.</p>",
